                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14123820" author="JIRAUSER308715" created="Fri, 5 Sep 2014 23:39:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think this is supposed to be:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;alter type foo rename somefield to bar;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At least in the spec it only lets you change a field name.  Not the type name.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-2.1.0/doc/cql3/CQL.textile&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-2.1.0/doc/cql3/CQL.textile&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&amp;lt;alter-type-stmt&amp;gt; ::= ALTER TYPE &amp;lt;typename&amp;gt; &amp;lt;instruction&amp;gt;

&amp;lt;instruction&amp;gt; ::= ALTER &amp;lt;field-name&amp;gt; TYPE &amp;lt;type&amp;gt;
                | ADD &amp;lt;field-name&amp;gt; &amp;lt;type&amp;gt;
                | RENAME &amp;lt;field-name&amp;gt; TO &amp;lt;field-name&amp;gt; ( AND &amp;lt;field-name&amp;gt; TO &amp;lt;field-name&amp;gt; )*
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14123831" author="rhatch" created="Fri, 5 Sep 2014 23:45:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We&apos;ve got some dtests from the past that successfully used the type rename syntax so I just want to be sure it&apos;s not a bug.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If the syntax is no longer supported I will adjust the tests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;/cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=slebresne&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;slebresne&quot;&gt;slebresne&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14123886" author="brandon.williams" created="Sat, 6 Sep 2014 00:30:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;At the least the cqlsh completion is wrong since it suggests TO after RENAME.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14124395" author="slebresne" created="Sat, 6 Sep 2014 08:30:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We&apos;ve removed type renames for now (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6940&quot; title=&quot;Consider removing user types rename for now&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-6940&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-6940&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but it&apos;s possible the cqlsh completion needs to be updated) so the error message of the description is correct. We do still support renaming fields inside a type though.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14124733" author="mishail" created="Sun, 7 Sep 2014 01:46:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m attaching a patch to adjust cqlsh tab-completion&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14124745" author="iamaleksey" created="Sun, 7 Sep 2014 02:46:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14124747" author="mishail" created="Sun, 7 Sep 2014 02:58:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed, thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14126318" author="rhatch" created="Mon, 8 Sep 2014 23:43:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;dtests should be updated shortly to no longer attempt UDT rename and to add some field rename coverage.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
